Gary Morton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gary_Morton 0 Gary Morton (born Morton Goldaper; December 19, 1924 – March 30, 1999) was a Jewish American stand-up comedian, whose primary venues were hotels and resorts of the Borscht Belt in upstate New York. He was born in New York City.
